1.2.name: wordpress/hit-sniffer-blog-stats
1.2.description:
Hitsniffer analytics is a powerful, yet simple, real time website visitor activity tracker and monitoring tool. Monitor your visitors clicks live and get useful stats and data such as referrers, bounce rate, link quality, search keywords, technologies used, OS, browser, came from and geo location city and country A time graph and much more advanced features are available such as goals and campaigns tracker for calculating return on investment and ratio. All in a live stream. All that you have to do is open the dashboard section and watch your visitor stream. It works on both Blogs and Websites.

Hitsniffer Features

  • Unique live dashboard
  • Visitor's name tracking
  • View visitors in Map
  • Live chat with visitors feature and Live support button
  • Realtime visitors list and pages they visited
  • Audible New Visitor Notification
  • Top referrals and top keywords
  • Top exit and entry page reporting
    • <
